</p></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">24S4 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Detects that the roll drawer is open. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Frame drawer 1 open switch 1</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 24S4 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">FRA_DRA1_OPEN_SW1</compsignal></comp> 
</p></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">24S5 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Detects that the top cover is open. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Frame top door switch 2</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 24S5 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">FRA_TOP_DOOR_SW2</compsignal></comp> 
