</p></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">24S7 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Detects that the printhead maintenance door is open. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Frame Printhead maintenance door switch 2</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 24S6 </compcodenr><compsignal translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compsignal ">FRA_PHD_MAINT_DOOR_SW2</compsignal></comp> 
